{"tid":1078573,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"同事有首期，係到呻話錯失左買樓時機","createTime":"2019-03-26T11:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T05:35:06.000Z","uid":16740,"like":24,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"84635b49da011f3daed87001f5824fc04962b33c","tid":1078573,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:05:55.000Z","msg":"個同事30頭，結左婚有個4歲大既仔，一直都係大西北租緊私樓住，儲左60萬首期，打算樓價跌就買<br />\n<br />\n咁今日收工一齊搭車果陣，咁岩傾開樓價又回升<br />\n<br />\n佢就係到呻佢早幾個月樓價跌果陣後悔無人市<br />\n咁我之前有留意開樓價，早幾個月樓價跌果陣都有提佢去睇樓入市<br />\n<br />\n佢就一直話岩岩先開始跌，又話跌多啲先，點先轉眼之間，樓價又升過，今日收工果陣佢同我呻到眼泛淚光<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話有乜理由跌得幾個月又再升過，仲話已經同外父外母講左準備入市做業主，等一家人唔洗再捱貴租可以有個安樂窩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n愈講就喊得愈勁，流哂眼淚同鼻涕，仲hi撚到啲鼻涕落我到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁岩我身上又無紙巾，請問巴打邊隻牌子既紙巾好？"},{"pid":"37b1b99cae68c39cff833e60ea084744cf4d2426","tid":1078573,"uid":35746,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EHm0Txo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEHm0Txo.jpg&h=1bf2bc90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b924eb093e9ee234bc4f96483082faae2cf475ec","tid":1078573,"uid":47184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:08:29.000Z","msg":"用開temple"},{"pid":"950a6ff303c90b42e789332164a0bda8b0936e02","tid":1078573,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37b1b99cae68c39cff833e60ea084744cf4d2426","tid":1078573,"uid":35746,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EHm0Txo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEHm0Txo.jpg&h=1bf2bc90&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:45:19.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？"},{"pid":"fd3c8846ccf84821aca1761d22a5ddecc156713d","tid":1078573,"uid":52911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:14:53.000Z","msg":"信左連登班淡淡以為會繼續跌？"},{"pid":"d8b4328bd697eb2f4213c0ea6f0870dce4045dc3","tid":1078573,"uid":152104,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:27:10.000Z","msg":"60萬咁少數目<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe3c5b692aaf35b25b757ab07d3e810bdfbd533","tid":1078573,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:38:02.000Z","msg":"鬼叫自己廢. 唔識係出世前輪迴道揀早50 年出世咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf34958b746c7d0581cf7e46c0bf84df3a69ac8","tid":1078573,"uid":185647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:14:32.000Z","msg":"早排跌市都冇跌穿400萬，得60萬首期，可以買邊到？"},{"pid":"c4811800a133a9ca6bcaab776672393c88b42839","tid":1078573,"uid":228794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:16:28.000Z","msg":"60 萬..<br />\n<br />\n個仔都笑鳩你"},{"pid":"1f5ac214cc34ae94e5b549f07cc7f4f2e1b77fb5","tid":1078573,"uid":68556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:18:27.000Z","msg":"Tempo 出左櫻花味  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0f114cd6e81b388fe203022267f2e8dddcd11b","tid":1078573,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d8b4328bd697eb2f4213c0ea6f0870dce4045dc3","tid":1078573,"uid":152104,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:27:10.000Z","msg":"60萬咁少數目<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:25:08.000Z","msg":"平平地都夠買"},{"pid":"e3076663357b1d7a3038fa3482533951bd379f19","tid":1078573,"uid":217336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T16:17:14.000Z","msg":"60<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\